@startuml characterization
!include ../_includes/style.iuml
!include ../_includes/legend.iuml

title Characterization — runner → tree → staircase → scorers (single-pass)

package "src/main/modelhub/" {
  component "modelLogStore.ts\n(2026-05-23)\n• .ts/<file>.log\n  (llama-server stdout/stderr)\n• .ts/<file>.error\n  (timestamped failures)\n• 4 MiB rotation,\n  best-effort writes" as LOG_STORE
}

package "src/main/modelhub/routing/" {
  component "characterizeAll.ts\n(single-pass, 2026-05-23)\n• size-sorted enumeration\n• per model: test → if\n  freegen_text → project\n• skipProjection gate\n• silent fallback when\n  embedder unavailable" as ALL

  component "characterizeRunner.ts\n• ensureChatLive\n  (spawn llama-server\n  if needed)\n• build seams\n  (embed=undefined here,\n   runSandbox)\n• timeoutMs 600_000\n• runFreeGenGenerate\n• runFreeGenProject\n• resolveEmbedderFn" as RUNNER

  component "characterize.ts\n(R5 pass — 16 R5 axes,\nslice 6c collapse fr/en/zh,\nQCM aptitude)" as R5_RUN

  component "characterizeTree.ts\n• read R5 signature\n• gate branches\n  with θ_open\n• loop branches\n• free-gen TEXT only\n  (phase 1)" as TREE

  component "staircase.ts\n• CAT-style climb\n• early-stop on fail\n• Beta-Laplace\n  posterior mean" as STAIR

  package "scorers/" as SCORERS_PKG {
    component "_types.ts\n+ checkSpec.ts\n(runCheck dispatch)" as SCORER_CORE
    component "10 deterministic\nscorers\n(math, factual,\nlogic, longctx,\ninstruction, meta, …)" as DET_SCORERS
    component "4 axis scorers\n(tooluse, robustness,\ncalibration,\nsummarization)" as AXIS_SCORERS
    component "informatics scorer\n(network/OS/sec/hw/theory)" as INFO_SCORER
    component "sandbox-pending\nscorers\n(code-debug/fim/refactor)\n→ slice 2d" as PEND_SCORERS
  }

  component "freegen.ts\n(2-phase, 2026-05-22)\n• generateFreeGenText\n  (chat only, no embedder)\n• projectFreeGenText\n  (embedder only)" as FREEGEN
  component "embedderCli.ts\n(2026-05-23)\n• embedViaLlamaCli\n  (spawn → JSON → exit)\n• resolveEmbedderCliFn" as EMB_CLI
  component "sandbox/\n(slice 2d)\nindex → posix |\n      windows |\n      unsafe" as SANDBOX
  component "signatureStore.ts\n(read / write\n.ts/<file>.json)" as STORE
}

ALL --> RUNNER : per model:\nfull / gen / project-only
ALL --> EMB_CLI : resolveEmbedderCliFn()\n(once at bulk start)
ALL --> FREEGEN : runFreeGenProject\n(per-model after test)
RUNNER --> R5_RUN : R5 first\n(coarse pass)
RUNNER --> TREE : then tree\n(fine pass, R5-gated)
TREE --> FREEGEN : generateFreeGenText\n(phase 1 only — embed undefined)
TREE --> STAIR : per branch\n(opened only)
STAIR --> SCORER_CORE : runCheck(item.check)
SCORER_CORE --> DET_SCORERS
SCORER_CORE --> AXIS_SCORERS
SCORER_CORE --> INFO_SCORER
SCORER_CORE --> PEND_SCORERS
PEND_SCORERS --> SANDBOX : `runSandbox` seam\n(slice 2d)
RUNNER --> STORE : finalResult ↩\nsignature
TREE --> STORE : merge tree fields\n(scores_per_leaf,\nbranch_scores,\npasses_per_leaf,\nfreegen_text)
FREEGEN ..> STORE : patch with\ntopic_coverage_*

ALL ..> LOG_STORE : appendErrorLog(file, reason)
RUNNER ..> LOG_STORE : appendServerLog\n(via launch.ts logChunk hook)

note bottom of RUNNER
  Failure-isolated:
  R5 ✓ even if tree fails;
  tree ✓ even if freegen fails;
  staircase ✓ even if a leaf
  goes UNMEASURED (D12 prior);
  log/error append is best-effort
  (a disk error never sinks a run).
end note

note right of STAIR
  étape 1 (Beta-Laplace):
  leaf_score = (1+passes)/(2+asked)
  3/3 ⇒ 0.80, never 1.0 in Phase A.
  Phase B saturation = deferred.
end note

note right of ALL
  Single-pass loop, per model:
  1. test (llama-server, no embedder)
  2. if freegen_text present
     AND skipProjection=false
     AND embedder available
     → spawn llama-embedding (CLI),
       project, exit.
  3. next model.
  RAM returns to ~0 between models.
end note

@enduml
